## Componentes Avanzados (wo-components/)

### wo-teseracto (Logo Animado)
```javascript
WoTeseracto.create('#container', {
  variant: 'architect-pulse',  // 'minimal', 'architect', 'pulse', 'architect-pulse'
  color: '#FFCB00',
  autoPlay: true,
  drawDuration: 2000,
  pulseDuration: 3000
});
```

### wo-flow-diagram (Diagrama de Flujo)
```javascript
initWoFlowDiagram('container-id', {
  preset: 'automation',  // o 'growth', custom
  autoPlay: true,
  animationSpeed: 1800,
  showControls: false
});
```

### wo-mapbox (Tema de Mapa)
Usa los tokens de `wo-tokens.css`:
```css
--map-background: #1a1a1e;
--map-water: #0A1628;
--map-building-fill: #2a2a2f;
--map-road-motorway: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.55);
/* ... ver wo-tokens.css para lista completa */
```

### wo-chatbot (UI de Chat)
```html
<div class="wo-chatbot" data-variant="compact">
  <div class="wo-chatbot__messages">...</div>
  <div class="wo-chatbot__input">...</div>
</div>
```

### wo-scoring-gauge (Indicador Circular)
```javascript
WoScoringGauge.create('#gauge-container', {
  score: 85,
  maxScore: 100,
  animated: true
});
```

